### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@email = alice@example.com
@password = password123

### 1. Sign up
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "displayName": "Alice"
}

### 2. Log in (copy token from response into @token below)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 3. Get current user (replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE)
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Negative test — no token → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
